org.apache.poi.ss.formula

Class WorkbookEvaluator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.poi.ss.formula.WorkbookEvaluator

  • @Internal
public final class WorkbookEvaluator
extends java.lang.Object
    Evaluates formula cells.

    For performance reasons, this class keeps a cache of all previously calculated intermediate cell values. Be sure to call clearAllCachedResultValues() if any workbook cells are changed between calls to evaluate~ methods on this class.
    For POI internal use only

    (评估公式单元格。出于性能原因，此类保留了之前计算出的所有中间像元值的缓存。如果在调用此类上的~方法之间更改了任何工作簿单元格，请务必调用clearAllCachedResultValues（）。仅供DOE内部使用)
    Author:
    Josh Micich, Thies Wellpott (debug output enhancements)

      • evaluate

        public ValueEval evaluate(java.lang.String formula,
                          CellReference target,
                          CellRangeAddressBase region)
        Some expressions need to be evaluated in terms of an offset from the top left corner of a region, such as some data validation and conditional format expressions, when those constraints apply to contiguous cells. When a relative formula is used, it must be evaluated by shifting by the target offset position relative to the top left of the range.

        Returns a single value e.g. a cell formula result or boolean value for conditional formatting.

        (当这些约束应用于连续单元格时，某些表达式需要根据区域左上角的偏差来评估，例如一些数据验证和条件格式表达式。当使用相对公式时，必须通过相对于范围左上角移动目标偏差位置来计算它。返回单个值，例如单元格公式结果或条件格式的布尔值。)
        Parameters:
        formula - The formula to evaluate(公式-要评估的公式)
        target - cell context for the operation(操作的目标单元上下文)
        region - containing the cell(区域-包含细胞)
        Returns:
        value(价值)
        Throws:
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - if target does not define a sheet name to evaluate the formula on.(java.lang. IllegalArgument例外-如果目标没有定义要计算公式的工作表名称。)

      • adjustRegionRelativeReference

        protected boolean adjustRegionRelativeReference(Ptg[] ptgs,
                                                CellReference target,
                                                CellRangeAddressBase region)
        Adjust formula relative references by the offset between the start of the given region and the given target cell. That is, treat the region top-left cell as "A1" for the purposes of evaluating relative reference components (row and/or column), and further move references by the position of the target within the region. 

        formula ref + range top-left + current cell range offset

        which simplifies to 

        formula ref + current cell ref

        (通过给定区域的起点和给定目标单元格之间的偏差调整公式相对引用。也就是说，为了评估相对参考分量（行和/或列），将区域左上角单元格视为“A1”，并根据区域内目标的位置进一步移动参考。公式参考+左上角范围+当前单元格范围补偿，简化为公式参考+当前单元格参考)
        Parameters:
        ptgs -(PTgs -)
        target - cell within the region to use.(目标-区域内要使用的细胞。)
        region - containing the cell, OR, for conditional format rules with multiple ranges, the region with the top-left-most cell(区域-包含单元格OR，对于具有多个范围的条件格式规则，具有最左上方单元格的区域)
        Returns:
        true if any Ptg references were shifted(如果任何Ptg参考发生变化，则为真)
        Throws:
        java.lang.IndexOutOfBoundsException - if the resulting shifted row/column indexes are over the document format limits(java.lang. IndexOutOfBoundsResponse-如果产生的移动行/列索引超过文档格式限制)
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - if target is not within region.(java.lang. IllegalArgument异常-如果目标不在区域内。)

      • setIgnoreMissingWorkbooks

        public void setIgnoreMissingWorkbooks(boolean ignore)
        Whether to ignore missing references to external workbooks and use cached formula results in the main workbook instead.

        In some cases exetrnal workbooks referenced by formulas in the main workbook are not avaiable. With this method you can control how POI handles such missing references:

        • by default ignoreMissingWorkbooks=false and POI throws CollaboratingWorkbooksEnvironment.WorkbookNotFoundException if an external reference cannot be resolved
        • if ignoreMissingWorkbooks=true then POI uses cached formula result that already exists in the main workbook
        (是否忽略缺少的对外部工作簿的引用，而改用主工作簿中的缓存公式结果。在某些情况下，主工作簿中的公式引用的外部工作簿不可用。使用此方法，您可以控制兴趣点如何处理此类缺失的引用：默认情况下，SEARCH reMissingWorkbooks = true，并且兴趣点会引发PartneratingWorkbooksEnvironment. WorkbookNotFoundExcellent如果SEARCH reMissingWorkbooks =true，那么兴趣点会使用主工作簿中已经存在的缓存公式结果)
        Parameters:
        ignore - whether to ignore missing references to external workbooks(忽略-是否忽略对外部工作簿的缺失引用)
        See Also:
        Bug 52575 for details
